#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:5
msgid "Feed exports"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:9
msgid ""
"One of the most frequently required features when implementing scrapers is "
"being able to store the scraped data properly and, quite often, that means "
"generating a \"export file\" with the scraped data (commonly called \"export "
"feed\") to be consumed by other systems."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:14
msgid ""
"Scrapy provides this functionality out of the box with the Feed Exports, "
"which allows you to generate a feed with the scraped items, using multiple "
"serialization formats and storage backends."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:21
msgid "Serialization formats"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:23
msgid ""
"For serializing the scraped data, the feed exports use the :ref:`Item "
"exporters <topics-exporters>` and these formats are supported out of the box:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:26
msgid ":ref:`topics-feed-format-json`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:27
msgid ":ref:`topics-feed-format-jsonlines`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:28
msgid ":ref:`topics-feed-format-csv`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:29
msgid ":ref:`topics-feed-format-xml`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:31
msgid ""
"But you can also extend the supported format through the :setting:"
"`FEED_EXPORTERS` setting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:37
msgid "JSON"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:39
msgid ":setting:`FEED_FORMAT`: ``json``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:40
msgid "Exporter used: :class:`~scrapy.contrib.exporter.JsonItemExporter`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:41
msgid ""
"See :ref:`this warning <json-with-large-data>` if you're using JSON with "
"large feeds"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:46
msgid "JSON lines"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:48
msgid ":setting:`FEED_FORMAT`: ``jsonlines``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:49
msgid "Exporter used: :class:`~scrapy.contrib.exporter.JsonLinesItemExporter`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:54
msgid "CSV"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:56
msgid ":setting:`FEED_FORMAT`: ``csv``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:57
msgid "Exporter used: :class:`~scrapy.contrib.exporter.CsvItemExporter`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:62
msgid "XML"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:64
msgid ":setting:`FEED_FORMAT`: ``xml``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:65
msgid "Exporter used: :class:`~scrapy.contrib.exporter.XmlItemExporter`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/feed-exports.rst:70
